Package pl.kasprowski.etcal.filters

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Filter
    Interface for all filters
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AoiMedianizeFilter
    Takes all subsequent readings with the same target, calculates median value for each variable and replaces all these readings by one median reading.
    MedianFilter
    For every reading calculates median of all variables taking into account len neighboring readings
    ReduceFilter
    For every len DataUnit objects calculates median of all variables and reduces it to one medianized DataUnit
